@startuml
title UC-15 Accept Emergency SOS - Activity Diagram

|System|
start
:Broadcast emergency SOS alert;

|Garage Owner|
:Receive emergency request;
:Review customer location and issue;

if (Accept emergency?) then (Yes)

  |System|
  :Check if already assigned;

  if (Already assigned?) then (Yes)
    :Display "Assignment Unavailable";

    stop
  else (No)
    :Lock assignment;

    |Garage Owner|
    :Select available mechanic;

    |Mechanic|
    :Receive assignment notification;
    :Open navigation;

    :Travel to customer location;

    |System|
    :Enable live GPS tracking;

    |Mechanic|
    :Send live GPS updates;

    |Customer|
    :Track mechanic location;

    |Mechanic|
    :Mark arrival;
    :Perform repair;
    :Mark repair complete;

    |System|
    :Update emergency status to COMPLETED;

    stop
  endif

else (No)

  :Ignore request;
  stop

endif

@enduml
